rows.label: qst201612_msg0001
rows.name:
Listen everyone, mo! We got
permission from the capital
to hold the concert, mo!

rows.label: qst201612_msg0002
rows.name:
With an unprecedented number of
guests and scale, it will be the
biggest concert in history, mo!

rows.label: qst201612_msg0004
rows.name: Is Pi TRYING to scare Nanakoori...?

rows.label: qst201612_msg0005
rows.name:
My apologies, mo. I got
a little excited, mo.

rows.label: qst201612_msg0006
rows.name:
Anyway, the preparations for the
concert will be ready soon, mo!

rows.label: qst201612_msg0007
rows.name: Everyone, let's get fired up, mo!

rows.label: qst201612_msg0008
rows.name:
...Mmm... ...Am I really
going to be okay?

rows.label: qst201612_msg0010
rows.name:
That's right. Just sing
like you always do.

rows.label: qst201612_msg0012
rows.name:
Then, Teetapz will go to Jakolo's
Inn in Alba Margen first, mo. I've
secured it as a dressing room, mo.

rows.label: qst201612_msg0013
rows.name:
Nanakoori-san, please come
when you're ready, mo.

rows.label: qst201612_msg0014
rows.name:
I have something to discuss,
so please bring her here, mo.
